th long‑standing farmers in Northern California, a region renowned for its ideal growing conditions and rich agricultural heritage. By partnering with these experienced cultivators, we ensure that our products are of the highest quality, grown with care and expertise. Our commitment to these farmers helps sustain local agriculture and supports the community by creating jobs and fostering economic growth.</p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-41_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-42_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="bfe68da6-1c32-4e84-8fea-4c26f324c646" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>Are Happie beverages vegan and gluten-free?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-44_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-45_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-46_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-2c70ea11-49b7-448e-8729-2a519a0ce8af"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Yes, all Happie beverages are vegan and gluten-free. We use natural ingredients, including agave nectar as a sweetener, to ensure our drinks align with various dietary preferences.</span></p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-57_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-58_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="af0bef60-6b48-4ce9-9d57-c60dbb182304" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>How should I store Happie beverages?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-60_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-61_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-62_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-6b48bce9-5d57-460d-bb18-23040141e5c1"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Store Happie beverages in a cool, dry place. For optimal taste, we recommend refrigerating them before consumption.</span></p></div></div></div></details></div></div><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-65_"><div data-pf-type="HTML.Video3" class="sc-cXPBhi jNGdCp pf-66_"><div class="pf-lazy-html-video pf-video-wrapper"><video data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/f7bf56b1b36645b6a495eb05544a376a.mp4#t=0.1" data-autoplay="false" data-lazyloading="lazy" width="100%" class="pf-visibility-hidden pf-media-video" type="video/1" controlsList="nodownload" d