QNK pf-70_ pf-heading-1-h2">THC-Infused Beverages</h2><div class="sc-gOqwAI hmpIDk pf-72_ pf-icon-left" data-scroll-to-top="true" data-open-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3"><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-73_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-74_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="ead6b6aa-2d69-43cb-9d6f-5b08b24ae994" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>What are Happie THC-infused beverages?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-76_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-77_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-78_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Our THC-infused beverages contain 5mg of hemp-derived Delta-9 THC and 5mg of CBD per serving, offering a balanced and enjoyable experience. They are designed as a sophisticated alternative to traditional alcoholic drinks.</p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-80_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-81_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="cb1d6f5b-08b2-4ae9-945e-2298a2aa3734" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>Will I feel "high" after consuming a THC-infused beverage?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-83_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-84_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-85_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-08b24ae9-945e-4298-a2aa-3734c4debac8"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">The 1:1 ratio of THC to CBD provides a mild, calming effect. Individual experiences may vary, so we recommend starting with one can to assess your personal tolerance.How long does it take to feel the effects?Effects typically begin within 10–20 minutes and can last up to 2 hours, depending on individual metabolism and tolerance.</span></p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-88_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-89_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="945e2298-a2aa-4734-84de-bac8154f3857" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>Are THC-infused beverages legal in my state?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-91_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-92_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-93_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-a2aa3734-c4de-4ac8-954f-3857f6b1daa1"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Hemp-derived THC products are federally legal under the 2018 Farm Bill, provided they contain no more than 0.3% THC by dry weight. However, state laws vary, so please check your local regulations before purchasing.</span></p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-96_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-97_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="c4debac8-154f-4857-b6b1-daa17613b8e5" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>Can I drive after consuming a THC-infused beverage?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-99_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-100_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-101_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-154f3857-f6b1-4aa1-b613-b8e515c59f5c"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">No. THC can impair your ability to operate vehicles or machinery. Please wait until the effects have fully subsided before driving.</span></p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-104_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-105_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="a6273dc2-766f-4a0a-a17c-d84532f3e48a" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>Will THC-infused beverages show up on a drug test?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-107_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-108_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-109_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-766f6a0a-617c-4845-b2f3-e48aa53f7858"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Yes. Consuming THC-infused beverages can result in a positive drug test for THC.</span></p></div></div></div></details></div></div><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-112_"><img alt="happie-about-flavors.png__PID:ae9118a8-d101-467f-8fb8-ec66f6e378e9" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-about-flavors.png?v=1755632543&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-about-flavors.png?v=1755632543&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-about-flavors.png?v=1755632543&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-about-flavors.png?v=1755632543&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-about-flavors.png?v=1755632543&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-about-flavors.png?v=1755632543&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-about-flavors.png?v=1755632543&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-about-flavors.png?v=1755632543&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-about-flavors.png?v=1755632543&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-about-flavors.png?v=1755632543&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-about-flavors.png?v=1755632543&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1.1785095320623917" width="680" height="577" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-lmUbDS jhRUAf pf-113_ pf-image-1" store="[object Object]"/></div></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-d87f" data-category="Sales Boost" data-name="Amigo" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-114_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section