g class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>What are functional mushroom beverages?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-123_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-124_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-125_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Our functional mushroom beverages are non-psychoactive drinks infused with adaptogenic mushrooms like Lion’s Mane, Cordyceps, and Reishi. They are designed to support focus, energy, and relaxation.</p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-127_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-128_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="ce2e9e8b-38e0-40ad-84f5-c6a7304e94e0" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>Do these beverages contain caffeine?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-130_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-131_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-132_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-38e070ad-04f5-46a7-b04e-94e09261475d"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">No, our functional mushroom beverages are caffeine-free, providing a natural alternative for sustained energy and mental clarity without the jitters.</span></p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-135_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-136_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="04f5c6a7-304e-44e0-9261-475d310ce827" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>What benefits do the mushrooms provide?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-138_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-139_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-140_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-304e94e0-9261-475d-b10c-e8273c1b323f"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Lion’s Mane, Cordyceps, and Reishi each bring unique benefits that work together to support balance and well-being. Lion’s Mane is known for enhancing cognitive function and mental clarity, helping keep the mind sharp and focused. Cordyceps naturally boosts energy and stamina, making it easier to power through the day. Meanwhile, Reishi promotes relaxation and stress reduction, creating a sense of calm and restoring balance to both body and mind.</span></p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-143_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-144_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="9261475d-310c-4827-bc1b-323fa1dea386" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>Are functional mushroom beverages safe for daily consumption?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-146_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-147_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-148_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-310ce827-3c1b-423f-a1de-a3863b180e4e"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Yes, our beverages are formulated for daily use. However, if you have specific health concerns or are taking medication, consult with a healthcare professional before adding new supplements to your routine.</span></p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-151_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-152_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="780927ed-1cff-4111-9f70-7e7b0aa394ac" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>Do functional mushroom beverages have a mushroom taste?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-154_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-155_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-156_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-1cff6111-1f70-4e7b-8aa3-94acd634d37d"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">No, our beverages are flavor-forward, masking any earthy mushroom taste with delicious fruit flavors like Mango Mimosa, Blue Razzberry, and Watermelon.</span></p></div></div></div></details></div></div><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-159_"><img alt="happie-about-b