ass="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-161_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-162_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-favicon-580C15.png?v=1754765231&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-favicon-580C15.png?v=1754765231&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-favicon-580C15.png?v=1754765231&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-favicon-580C15.png?v=1754765231&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-favicon-580C15.png?v=1754765231&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-favicon-580C15.png?v=1754765231&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-favicon-580C15.png?v=1754765231&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-favicon-580C15.png?v=1754765231&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-favicon-580C15.png?v=1754765231&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-favicon-580C15.png?v=1754765231&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0640/2431/3942/files/happie-favicon-580C15.png?v=1754765231&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image5" class="sc-fscnvs dncZrx pf-163_ pf-image-1" store="[object Object]"/><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-164_ pf-heading-1-h2">Additional Information</h2><div class="sc-gOqwAI hmpIDk pf-166_ pf-icon-left" data-scroll-to-top="true" data-open-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3"><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-167_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-168_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="06730bdf-8a89-4f44-9625-7556b92ba2b4" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>Are Happie beverages suitable for pregnant or nursing individuals?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-170_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-171_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-172_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">We advise against consuming our THC-infused beverages if you are pregnant or nursing. For our functional mushroom beverages, consult with a healthcare professional before consumption.</p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-174_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-175_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="44162575-56b9-4ba2-b479-c35f118e7d5f" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>Will I feel "high" after consuming a THC-infused beverage?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-177_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-178_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-179_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-56b92ba2-b479-435f-918e-7d5f416d6927"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">The 1:1 ratio of THC to CBD provides a mild, calming effect. Individual experiences may vary, so we recommend starting with one can to assess your personal tolerance.How long does it take to feel the effects?Effects typically begin within 10–20 minutes and can last up to 2 hours, depending on individual metabolism and tolerance.</span></p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-182_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-183_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="b479c35f-118e-4d5f-816d-6927c931c3c9" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>Can I mix Happie beverages with alcohol?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-185_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-186_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-187_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-118e7d5f-416d-4927-8931-c3c960d9845b"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">We do not recommend mixing our beverages with alcohol, especially the THC-infused line, as it can intensify effects and impair judgment.</span></p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-190_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-191_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="416d6927-c931-43c9-a0d9-845b396c6fdd" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>How many calories are in a Happie beverage?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-193_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-194_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-195_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-c931c3c9-60d9-445b-b96c-6fdd64d7118f"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Each Happie beverage contains approximately 30 - 40 calories, making them a lighter alternative to many traditional drinks.</span></p></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-198_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-199_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="60d9845b-396c-4fdd-a4d7-118fd579a2af" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-plus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V224H48c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32H192V432c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V288H400c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H256V80z"></path></svg><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-minus pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M432 256c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32L48 288c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32l352 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32z"></path></svg><span>Do Happie beverages contain any artificial sweeteners?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-201_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-202_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-203_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-396c6fdd-64d7-418f-9579-a2af33a2471b"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">No, we use agave nectar as a natural sweetener in our beverages.</span></p></div></div></div></details></div></div><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-206_"><div data-pf-type="HTML.Video3" class="sc-cXPBhi jNGdCp pf-207_"><div class="pf-lazy-html-video pf-video-wrapper"><video data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/6f6125457680466e99db4710f80dca2e.mp4#t=0.1" data-autopla